- [ ] Correct PF component for the use case
- [ ] Layout uses PageSection / Flex / Gallery (not raw divs)
- [ ] All styling uses PF CSS tokens (no hardcoded px/colors)
- [ ] Works in dark mode
- [ ] Responsive behavior tested
- [ ] Keyboard navigable
- [ ] ARIA labels on icon-only buttons
- [ ] Loading / error / empty states

